WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.220
Fully funded scholarship to study Romania.

00:00:02.221 --> 00:00:04.141
Scholarship is strictly for citizens of no N,

00:00:04.142 --> 00:00:05.421
I U, Nigeria, Ghana,

00:00:05.422 --> 00:00:06.701
Kenya, etcetera.

00:00:06.702 --> 00:00:07.821
The scholarship covers tuition,

00:00:07.822 --> 00:00:09.541
accommodation and monthly allowance.

00:00:09.542 --> 00:00:12.341
To apply, you only need to upload C V motivation letter,

00:00:12.342 --> 00:00:14.681
recommendation letter. No English test required.

00:00:14.682 --> 00:00:17.741
The best part is Romania says apply for the scholarship first.

00:00:17.742 --> 00:00:18.861
If you get the scholarship,

00:00:18.862 --> 00:00:20.781
then you can go ahead and apply for admission.

00:00:20.782 --> 00:00:23.061
Go to Google and search Romania Government Scholarship.

00:00:23.062 --> 00:00:24.381
Then click on the official website.

00:00:24.382 --> 00:00:26.141
This scholarship is available for Bachelor's,

00:00:26.142 --> 00:00:27.741
Masters and P a G programmes.

00:00:27.742 --> 00:00:29.261
First year you'll be taught in Romania

00:00:29.262 --> 00:00:31.341
since majority of the programmes are in Romania.

00:00:31.342 --> 00:00:32.741
But apply is absolutely free.

00:00:32.742 --> 00:00:34.511
Read caption and other update shed.
